## Also fix вҖ” AppLayout null guard (`src/components/navigation/AppLayout.tsx`)

Line 67: `if (!userType || !profile) return null;`

If `user_type` is missing (edge case вҖ” old accounts before the trigger existed), this renders a blank screen. Change to:

```tsx
if (!profile) return null;
const resolvedUserType = userType ?? "creator"; // safe default
```

Pass `resolvedUserType` to ProfileDrawer and MainSidebar instead of `userType`.

